[SN]TITLE[SN]
In pictures: Your wolf encounters

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
They feature frequently in folklore, but how easy is it to spot wolves? We asked you to share your photos of the wolves you've seen around the world. Here's just a selection of some of your amazing images.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The last wolf in the UK was shot centuries ago, but now a "rewilding" process could see them return to Scotland. Adam Weymouth hiked across the Scottish Highlands in the footsteps of this lost species.
The place where wolves could soon return
